{"about_the_game":"Tired of low polished TD mobile game? Well, I was when I decided to work on Space Adventure TD.<br>Fan of the genre, I started playing TD back in Starcraft and Warcraft III and was disappointed to see TD migrating and be confined to mobile.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Space Adventure TD offers you:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A desktop 3D game, created with passion<br></li><li>A 20 levels campaign, story driven with 4 difficulty levels<br></li><li>2 challenge levels with ranked leaderboards<br></li><li>35 unique towers<br></li><li>70 upgrades<br></li><li>8 different biomes<br></li><li>Skillpoints to use in order to boost and unblock towers (with real strategic choices)<br></li><li>2 languages available for now: English and French (more to come)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Why is the game in early access ?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The game needs calibration with regular patches before pretending to be finished<br></li><li>More languages will be added soon<br></li><li>Bugs will be found and they shall be fixed<br></li><li>More challenge levels will be created with specific leaderboards<br></li><li>Improving voices and some graphic elements</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Easy peasy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/923340/e493c007597a820c41e824b0735107ab5b4b7509.jpg"},{"name":"True savior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/923340/ca062b4b57996260b8c9c2e37a5b124af1f8bd52.jpg"},{"name":"Captain Earth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/923340/23eb054a92f45367f0fa2d149ae245ec642b3a6b.jpg"},{"name":"Hall of Fame","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/923340/bd6b48ecbe6ce4860e559990bb91f1d2e46ad95f.jpg"},{"name":"Strategist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/923340/655c95d2b1257e1a91691eb3fdad03de6e4b8aab.jpg"},{"name":"Come at me"